5. DUAL RAIL MODEL

Rail A: Consumer Fiat Flow

* Debit
* ACH
* Wallets
* Payroll
* Consumer payouts

Rail B: Treasury / Institutional

* Reserve liquidity
* Wire
* Interbank
* Government
* Federal settlement

Routing Logic:

IF transaction <= threshold:
    Consumer Rail
ELSE:
    Treasury Rail

